== 製作 ==
2019年8月21日，據報導，[[勞勃·羅里葛茲|勞勃·羅里葛茲]]將自編自導《全民小英雄》，由[[琵豔卡·喬普拉|琵豔卡·喬普拉·強納斯]]、[[克利斯汀·史萊特|克利斯汀·史萊特]]和[[佩德羅·帕斯卡|佩德羅·帕斯卡]]等人主演<ref name="WWBH">{{cite web|first=Andreas|last=Wiseman|title=Priyanka Chopra Jonas To Star In Netflix Superhero Movie From 'Alita: Battle Angel' Director Robert Rodriguez|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/priyanka-chopra-jonas-netflix-superhero-movie-robert-rodriguez-1202700678/|date=2019-08-21|website=[[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]]|access-date=2020-01-22|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227003141/https://deadline.com/2019/08/priyanka-chopra-jonas-netflix-superhero-movie-robert-rodriguez-1202700678/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；電影由羅里葛茲的{{le|麻煩製造者工作室|Troublemaker Studios}}製作，[[Netflix|Netflix]]發行。[[主要拍攝|主要拍攝]]於2019年8月在[[德克薩斯州|德克薩斯州]]進行。<ref name="moredevelopments">{{cite web|first=Dino-Ray|last=Ramos|title=Christian Slater, YaYa Gosselin, Akira Akbar, Pedro Pascal And More Join Robert Rodriguez's 'We Can Be Heroes' At Netflix|url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/christian-slater-yaya-gosselin-akira-akbar-join-robert-rodriguezs-we-can-be-heroes-netflix-1202701061/|date=2019-08-21|website=Deadline Hollywood|access-date=2020-01-21|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227003117/https://deadline.com/2019/08/christian-slater-yaya-gosselin-akira-akbar-join-robert-rodriguezs-we-can-be-heroes-netflix-1202701061/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 發行 ==
《全民小英雄》於2020年12月25日在{{lang|en|Netflix}}上線<ref>{{cite web |url=https://collider.com/we-can-be-heroes-trailer-netflix-sharkboy-and-lavagirl/ |title='We Can Be Heroes' Takes Us Back to the World of 'Sharkboy and Lavagirl' |first=Matt |last=Goldberg |website=[[Collider|Collider]] |date=2020-12-04 |accessdate=2020-12-04 |archive-date=2020-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227003129/https://collider.com/we-can-be-heroes-trailer-netflix-sharkboy-and-lavagirl/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>；原本的發行日為2021年1月1日<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/1154701-we-can-be-heroes-first-look-photos |title='We Can Be Heroes' First-Look Photos Released for Robert Rodriguez's Superhero Movie |website=ComingSoon.net |first=Kylie |last=Hemmert |date=2020-11-12 |accessdate=2020-12-05 |archive-date=2020-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227003141/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/1154701-we-can-be-heroes-first-look-photos |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 反響 ==
[[匯總媒體|匯總媒體]]網站[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]基於39條評論，該片持有69%的新鮮度，平均評分為6.29／10；該網站共識：「儘管對成年人來說可能太過瘋狂，但《全民小英雄》將其精緻的主題與熱情和熱忱的創意相結合。」<ref>{{cite web |title= We Can Be Heroes (2020) |url= https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/we_can_be_heroes_2021 |website= [[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |access-date= 2021-01-07 |archive-date= 2020-12-27 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201227003117/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/we_can_be_heroes_2021 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。電影在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根據9位評論家的評論而得53分<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/we-can-be-heroes |title=We Can Be Heroes Reviews |website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |access-date=2021-01-01 |archive-date=2020-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227003123/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/we-can-be-heroes |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《全民小英雄》上線後獲得4400萬家庭的關注，在其88個國家的兒童總體名單中排名第一。<ref name="Deadline(2021-01-04)" />

